name: Kasadya Ning Taknaa (Psychedlic Budots Version)
description:
Audio is a psychedelic remix of Dj Jansnow's Budot remix of "Kasadya Ning Taknaa" the classic Cebuano Christmas song that is the basis for the classic "Ang Pakso ay Sumapit." 

The visuals gets its cues from karaoke aesthetics along with Christmas decorations. 

The character is inspired by my yearly tradition of making callos for Noche buena.
